                  <additions><!--THIS element in domlib CONTAINS ESCAPED HTML, thus it is not possible to reliably extract the information about pages. Please watch out.-->
                     <list>
                        <item xml:id="a1">
                           <locus/><p><span style="font-size: small;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: ">Fol. 31rb (above): Donation note.</span></span></p><q xml:lang="gez"><p style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: ">Fol. 31rb:</span></span><span lang="EN-US" unicode="" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:&#10;115%;font-family:"> </span><span style="font-size: large;"><span lang="AMH" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: Nyala;">&#4829;&#4757;&#4721;&#4961; &#4632;&#4925;&#4624;&#4941;&#4961; &#4824;&#4808;&#4608;&#4710;&#4961; &#4848;&#4869;&#4843;&#4829;&#4635;&#4733;&#4961; &#4928;&#4624;&#4840;&#4961; &#4621;&#4851;&#4961; &#4616;&#4632;&#4677;&#4848;&#4661;&#4961; &#4912;&#4651;&#4677;&#4618;&#4902;&#4661;&#4968; &#4808;&#4824;&#4808;&#4608;&#4710;&#4961; &#4779;&#4621;&#4819;&#4961; &#4757;&#4811;&#4840;&#4968; &#4723;&#4710;&#4725;&#4961; &#4971;&#4624;&#4653;&#4961; &#4704;&#4653;&#4758;&#4661;&#4961; &#4925;&#4811;&#4821;&#4961; &#4970;&#4829;&#4941;&#4677;&#4961; &#4616;&#4632;&#4875;&#4648;&#4835;&#4961; &#4637;&#4757;&#4851;&#4941;&#4961; &#4969;&#4632;&#4875;&#4648;&#4835;&#5011; &#4835;&#4835;&#5011; &#4971;&#4672;&#4634;&#4661;&#4961; &#4853;&#4707;&#4709;&#4961; &#4840;&#4611;&#4617;&#4961; &#4637;&#4661;&#4616;&#4961; &#4872;&#4709;&#4649;&#4961; &#4872;&#4709;&#4648;&#4961; &#4768;&#4707;&#4961; &#4720;&#4781;&#4616;&#4961; &#4611;&#4845;&#4635;&#4758;&#4725;&#4961; &#4768;&#4636;&#4757;&#4961;</span></span></p></q>
                           <q xml:lang="en"/>
                           <p>The note, written in Gǝʿǝz with a few words in Amharic (in the main hand?), mentions däğğazmač Ḍäḥayä Lǝda as the one who donated the book, together with other items (curtains, vessels, etc.), to the church of Ṗäraqliṭos.</p>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a2">
                           <locus/><p><span style="font-size: small;"><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: ">Fol. 31rb (below): Gw&#601;lt-charter (continuation of Additio 1). </span></span></p><q xml:lang="gez"><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; text-align: left;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:10.0pt;&#10;font-family:">Fol. 31rb: </span><span style="font-size: large;"><span lang="AMH" style="font-family: Nyala;">&#4808;&#4885;&#4621;&#4720;&#4961; &#4824;&#4880;&#4616;&#4721;&#4961; &#4789;&#4622;&#4633;&#4961; &#4848;&#4674;&#4673;&#4961; &#4616;&#4872;&#4709;&#4648;&#4961; &#4768;&#4637;&#4619;&#4781;&#4961; &#4720;&#4875;&#4706;&#4774;&#4633;&#4961; &#4819;&#4706;&#4845;&#4961; &#4808;&#4757;&#4769;&#4661;&#4961; &#4704;&#4824;&#4632;&#4752;&#4961; &#4632;&#4757;&#4877;&#4645;&#4721;&#4961; &#4616;&#4757;&#4873;&#4645;&#4752;&#4961; &#4846;&#4624;&#4757;&#4661;&#4961; &#4632;&#4941;&#4672;&#4652;&#4961; &#4773;&#4877;&#4826;&#4768;&#4709;&#4628;&#4653;&#4961; &#4624;&#4848;&#4657;&#4961; &#4808;&#4880;&#4616;&#4721;&#4961; &#4808;&#4768;&#4813;&#4872;&#4825;&#4961; &#4704;&#4675;&#4616;&#4961; &#4975;&#4672;&#4658;&#4659;&#4757;&#4961; &#4776;&#4632;&#4961; &#4770;&#4845;&#4707;&#4821;&#4961; &#4629;&#4829;&#4709;&#4961; &#4824;&#4770;&#4720;&#4637;&#4613;&#4648;&#4961; &#4773;&#4757;&#4704;&#4616;&#4961; &#4779;&#4613;&#4755;&#4725;&#4961; &#4707;&#4613;&#4722;&#4726;&#4633;&#4968; &#4776;&#4632;&#4961; &#4845;&#4777;&#4758;&#4633;&#4961; &#4819;&#4661;&#4704;&#4961; &#4704;&#4632;&#4757;&#4877;&#4645;&#4726;&#4961; </span><span lang="AMH" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: Nyala;">&#4656;&#4635;&#4843;&#4725;&#4961; &#4616;&#4819;&#4616;&#4632;&#4961; &#4819;&#4616;&#4637;&#4961; &#4768;&#4636;&#4757;&#4961;</span></span></p></q>
                           <q xml:lang="en"/>
                           <p>The note states that the land grant was issued by the “children” of Gäbrä ʾAmlak during the time of King Yoḥannǝs IV (r. 1872-89).</p>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="e1">- The title ጻድቃን is crudely written in yellow on the front cover.&#xD;
- Corrections (words or letters) written interlineally: fols. 5va, 13va, 14rb, 20rb, 27va. &#xD;
- Pen trails: fols. 1r, 1v, 2r, 2v.&#xD;
- Illegible recent note in pen on fol. 32v.&#xD;
- Drawing of St. Mary in black ink: fol. 1v.&#xD;
- Crude drawings and crude recent notes in pen: fols. 1v, 2r, 31v, 32r.</item>
                     </list>
